- Oh, it sure is.

532
00:30:34,804 --> 00:30:36,306
Especially with this mailbag.

533
00:30:36,802 --> 00:30:37,876
It does look heavy.

534
00:30:37,976 --> 00:30:40,774
If I'm all in now, I wonder what
I'm going to be like this afternoon.

535
00:30:41,047 --> 00:30:42,671
Well I guess I'll live.
- Yeah.

536
00:30:42,887 --> 00:30:45,795
With everything so high I've got to
keep my nose to the grindstone.

537
00:30:46,686 --> 00:30:48,531
I got a pension plan.
Did I tell you about it?

538
00:30:48,648 --> 00:30:49,520
Yes, you did.

539
00:30:49,653 --> 00:30:51,722
Well, you got to follow it to a T.

540
00:30:52,031 --> 00:30:53,075
Every penny counts.

541
00:30:53,435 --> 00:30:55,227
